---
title: Carb Smart Middle Eastern-Inspired Beef Koftas with Feta and Radish Salad
description: Tender shawarma-seasoned koftas are served alongside a hearty spring mix salad with a sweet yet tart fig dressing in this simple and filling Middle-Eastern-inspired dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/carb-smart-middle-eastern-inspired-beef-koftas-62bb507a.jpg
